{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Line a square cake tin (approx. 16 cm) with cling film.","Place cashew nuts in mixing bowl and grind <nobr>30 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add dates, raisins, cocoa and orange zest then blend <nobr>30 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then blend again <nobr>15 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Tip out into prepared tin and press down firmly with the back of a spoon. Chill in fridge for at least 2 hours.","Remove hardened mixture from tin and place on a chopping board. Slice into 12 bars. Wrap in cling film or greaseproof paper and store in fridge until required. Serve as a healthy, natural snack."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["160 g cashew nuts, raw","160 g medjool dates, pitted, halved","50 g raisins","4 Tbsp cocoa powder, unsweetened","2 oranges, finely grated zest only"]}],"id":"r143869","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-y41d9ytwy6U\/XZaqROWP6CI\/AAAAAAAAhbA\/I8Rc_6CQTr0qtKdbricSiQ99DDTe5P8RwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_TaBohLT0ED7MaN6l.png","title":"Cacao and Orange bars","publishedAt":"2017-04-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3.7 g","fat":"7.6 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"14.6 g","calories":"591 kJ \/ 141 kcal"},"usefulItems":"square cake tin (16 cm), cling film, airtight container, greaseproof paper, long sharp knife, chopping board, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["If mixture does not bind, add 1-2 tsp boiling water then mix again <strong>5 sec\/speed 4<\/strong>."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 15m","12 pieces"]}